preference.name: QRY_Audit_-_File_Access_Logs_SortKeys
preference.preference_description: Provides the keys used for sorting audit logs as a result of the execution of the saved query "Audit - File Access Logs". Valid value is fnd0LoggedDate(default value) attribute or any other attributes of interest of Audit Manager under the BO Fnd0AuditLog. The default value is to sort the results based on the property "fnd0LoggedDate".
